  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Some messages that had been sent to 1-1 and public chat have been lost. From the logs it looks that the clients time has drifted, so they are unable to communicate, so they would need to check that their clocks are synced. (It could also be that the mailserver clock has drifted, but probably less likely, worth checking though).\r\n\r\nBased on logs from mailserver it seems they are getting kicked because they have a time drift\r\n```\r\n\u001B[31mERROR\u001B[0m[04-19|11:04:12] bad envelope received, peer will be disconnected \u001B[31mpeer\u001B[0m=0a346f9db199cd6b \u001B[31merr\u001B[0m=\"envelope created in the future [ad7cd4aced574eb96b218d8204850c0bb51a995e4bc663d44ab3986833e52ed8]\"\r\n\u001B[31mERROR\u001B[0m[04-19|11:04:12] bad envelope received, peer will be disconnected \u001B[31mpeer\u001B[0m=0a346f9db199cd6b \u001B[31merr\u001B[0m=\"envelope created in the future [c3d288ace0ff9d865a81d769ec06f265e2c9049c8ce408363e7296704915344e]\"\r\n\u001B[31mERROR\u001B[0m[04-19|11:04:12] bad envelope received, peer will be disconnected \u001B[31mpeer\u001B[0m=0a346f9db199cd6b \u001B[31merr\u001B[0m=\"envelope created in the future [ee1793d02faf9c68b923f55ee3235528c78b4fe0aa8afd390236175c82b043de]\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open public chat\r\n- Try to send some messages\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, April 19\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
